summary: This mod add pets of different species (mostly dogs) to many NPCs in the different towns and cities.
descriptionHtml: This is a very early WIP but I wanted to upload the file because of all the work that has been put into it so far. This will be hidden until a future date at which I feel it is complete enough to offer. Obviously, this description will change before this file is available for download to the public.
